00:07:33.570 --> 00:07:34.990
Salut, fée !

00:07:34.990 --> 00:07:36.200
Condamner!

00:07:36.200 --> 00:07:38.410
--Luffy, es-tu vivant ?
--Quel sol de merde.

00:07:58.930 --> 00:08:00.340
Enfoiré!

00:08:17.450 --> 00:08:18.410
Hé!

00:08:18.410 --> 00:08:22.040
Devrions-nous aller dormir ?
Ouais.

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:24.080
